/-- The relation that one `simple_graph` is a subgraph of another.
Note that this should be spelled `‚â§`. -/
def is_subgraph (x y : simple_graph V) : Prop := ‚àÄ ‚¶Év w : V‚¶Ñ, x.adj v w ‚Üí y.adj v w

